originalText.text:
Extremely negative experience with Fatim Balde in the leasing office. Make me want to stay away from this building even before I apply. Pls be mentally prepared that you feel like you owe her money.

I asked for floorplan of a specific unit and she never send it. When I stop by the leasing office and ask if she has it, she says yes. I asked could u pls send to me, she says she doesn’t have A MIN to send yet. She promises to send me by tmwr noon but never sends it. EXTREMELY UNPROFESSIONAL.

originalText.text: My apartment has a view of this building - across the alley.  There is a window with pieces of typing paper stuck to it and a bedsheet haphazardly draped across part of the window. An eyesore.  Property management/owner is sketchy Foly Square Associates.  Building management does nothing about it. Sorry for anyone who actually lives in this building. Zero rating
